#ii)
f1 <- function(x){
  if(x<quantile(dat$Temp,0.25))
    {
      return("Low")
  }else if (x>quantile(dat$Temp,0.25) && x<quantile(dat$Temp,0.5)){
       return("Medium")
  }else if(x>quantile(dat$Temp,0.5) && x<quantile(x,0.75)){
       return("High")
     }else return("Extreme")
}
dat$Temp_4 <- sapply(dat$Temp,f1)
